o gozaimashita<br />\n陪佢返lobby企正個日本爸爸<br />\n佢眼骨骨大喝聲man dasu ka<br />\n阿女佢今年唔夠十六and a half<br />\n佢劍道十段話同我練下<br />\nsayonara 忍著淚說goodbye啦<br />\nthanks thanks thanks thanks monica<br />\n摸摸口袋駛剩八個幾咋<br />\n蝕埋份糧添呢次衰咗啦<br />\nsayonara 忍著淚說goodbye啦<br />\nthanks thanks thanks thanks monica<br />\n摸摸口袋駛剩八個幾咋<br />\n蝕埋份糧添呢次衰咗啦"},{"pid":"49e21a826e780fe1a2b2ca41c03e68a14acef762","tid":785862,"uid":74571,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T17:30:36.000Z","msg":"松板屋中那東京夢　聖子變作了舊時路標"},{"pid":"8d4f50468cdd2a9e2b26d7417a140dd57577fed7","tid":785862,"uid":69115,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"04d2102732663f5c5e728ca667a2276d4f7931bc","tid":785862,"uid":41375,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T16:25:37.000Z","msg":"尋晚喺東急碰正個日本娃娃"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T17:33:53.000Z","msg":"尋晚响東急見到套日本梳化<br />\n<br />\n個坐&ldquo;煎&rdquo;極大，仲有 seat belt 咁豪華<br />\n<br />\n仲可以攤開當床訓，唔係講假"},{"pid":"5ac30ea9511b06b378aa499591703812b292810b","tid":785862,"uid":102064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T17:41:29.000Z","msg":"你在何地 若然在札幌可想起我"},{"pid":"1b65e50df5f2df33146b044a4b39648a60bf5514","tid":785862,"uid":55280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T18:10:13.000Z","msg":"謝謝這涉谷中心 潮流百貨的密林"},{"pid":"f24fc36dc65f49cba3094334f4c381c24eb20f61","tid":785862,"uid":49004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T18:26:49.000Z","msg":"宇都宮 乳出驚人宇都宮<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bb9a56a1f7f46aecf5dbacf86c69d8d1caaaf39","tid":785862,"uid":38195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ac30ea9511b06b378aa499591703812b292810b","tid":785862,"uid":102064,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T17:41:29.000Z","msg":"你在何地 若然在札幌可想起我"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-19T18:30:45.000Z","msg":"寒命<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/fa